data.description: Perfectly priced meticulously maintained home. Make this beautiful, spacious, open floor plan your dream home. Charming living room, kitchen, and dining to enjoy and entertain your guests and family. Great layout with master bedroom located to the rear of home and the additional three bedrooms to the front of home.  Master bedroom has a large walk-in closet. Home features stainless steel refrigerator and stove. Washer and Dryer INCLUDED. Conveniently located near to Wal-Mart, Publix, and many restaurants. Auburndale boast parks, playgrounds, boating, swimming, shopping, fishing and easy access to Interstate 4. **$5000 towards buyers closing cost**.
